Package Network.messages

Class Message

java.lang.Object
Network.messages.Message
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Message extends Object implements Serializable
The Message class represents a serializable message used for socket communication. It encapsulates information to be sent between client and server via sockets.
